: red;\">希望雙方</span>按照他與特朗普達成的重要共識，促進中美關係健康穩定發展。<br />\n<br />\n(呢句說話唔尋常,乜雙方,暗示黨內有人唔聽佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n他表示重視與特朗普的良好關係，願與他在出席阿根廷二十國集團領導人峰會期間再次會晤，就中美關係及其他重大問題<span style=\"color: red;\">深入交換意見</span>。<br />\n<br />\n(即係唔會有協議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n習近平表示，兩人對中美關係健康穩定發展、擴大中美經貿合作都有<span style=\"color: red;\">良好的願望</span>，中美要努力把這種願望變為現實。<br />\n<br />\n即係發下夢先la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T19:31:05.000Z","msg":"外交辭令：充份交換意見=嘈得好勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5eda3287330bba8532cbb74c20ff43d19dcb865","tid":885800,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edd34d3284698dcbae30361a413a686545d2af71","tid":885800,"uid":39568,"like":51,"dislike":5,"score":46,"quote":{"pid":"e742d304fb50138849ea3e0bf4b9ffc667244931","tid":885800,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:15:22.000Z","msg":"Just had a long and very good conversation with President Xi Jinping of China. We talked about many subjects, with a heavy emphasis on Trade. Those discussions are moving along nicely with meetings being scheduled at the G-20 in Argentina. Also had good discussion on North Korea!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GJvcGzs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGJvcGzs.jpg&h=cf6d09a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:45:33.000Z","msg":"佢twitter講野唔好當真<br />\n<br />\n呢個只係成盤棋既其一步<br />\n<br />\n你睇返佢之呢一年黎既往績<br />\n<br />\n後續應該有啲爆野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:22:00.000Z","msg":"佢做d野都唔好當真"},{"pid":"ac7b828f45bc0f94643da019f5f6bff89b82aca0","tid":885800,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:31:30.000Z","msg":"11月6之前都會話中國就範喇，